      • getName

        public abstract net.proteusframework.core.locale.TextSource getName()
        A name reflecting the intended use of the configuration for an EmailTemplate. This is typically defined by the state of the EmailConfig. For example, if this configuration represents a Form, then the name would typically be the form name. If instead the configuration is programmatically defined, then the name would be defined by a person entering text to describe it's purpose.
        Returns:
        the name.
